We had perfect peace and quiet in a lovely room overlooking the central courtyard (away from the front street which does border onto the more 'lively' red light district).	We had a decent sized room overlooking the canal on the 1st floor, but it was really quiet and comfortable.	You are right in the center of Amsterdam, very close to red light district but set in a very secluded and quiet courtyard.	Although it is right next to the red light district, it is tucked away and is quiet and safe.	Location is great, on the edge of the red light district but lovely and peaceful.